OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784623688
OL,3,CNinth man charged in group-based child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation investigation
OL,6,FNine men have been charged with over
OL,7,F40 offences in an investigation into a
OL,8,Fgroup-based child sexual exploitation.
OL,10,FDetectives from Gwent Police carried
OL,11,Fout a targeted operation on 14 July to
OL,12,Farrest eight of the men, which
OL,13,Fincluded activity in Newport, Swansea,
OL,14,FLondon, Birmingham, Lancashire,
OL,15,FEdinburgh and the Argyll and Bute area
OL,16,Fin Scotland.
OL,18,FOn Friday 17 July, Gwent police
OL,19,Farrested the ninth man in Newport,
OL,20,FMohammad Ramzan, aged 76.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
