OL,3,CNinth man charged in group-based child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation investigation
OL,6,FMohammad was charged with seven
OL,7,Foffences, including:
OL,9,FThe Crown Prosecution Service has
OL,10,Fauthorised a total of 41 charges
OL,11,Fbetween the nine men.
OL,13,FThe investigation was part of
OL,14,FOperation Oak, which looked into
OL,15,Freports of sexual abuse made by women
OL,16,Fwho were children at the time of the
OL,17,Falleged offences between 1985 and 1996.
