OL,3,CNinth man charged in group-based child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation investigation
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent, Andrew
OL,7,FTuck said: "We continue to support the
OL,8,Fvictims in this case alongside
OL,9,Fspecialist agencies.
OL,11,F"At the heart of our investigation has
OL,12,Fbeen supporting victims. Together with
OL,13,Fspecialist agencies, we are continuing
OL,14,Fto provide support to them".
