OL,3,CNinth man charged in group-based child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation investigation
OL,6,FHe added: "I know investigations of
OL,7,Fthis nature are likely to cause
OL,8,Fconcern in our communities, but it's
OL,9,Fvital to the victims in this case and
OL,10,Fthe integrity of the investigation
OL,11,Fthat nothing in posted on social media
OL,12,Fwhich could impact the court
OL,13,Fproceedings.
