OL,3,CNinth man charged in group-based child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation investigation
OL,6,F"Anyone who reports child abuse will
OL,7,Fbe taken seriously, and we would urge
OL,8,Fanyone who has suffered abuse or has
OL,9,Fconcerns about someone who may be
OL,10,Fsuffering to come forward. We will
OL,11,Flisten to you and investigate all
OL,12,Foffences, and also ensure you have
OL,13,Faccess to any help or support you
OL,14,Fneed."
OL,16,FJenny Hopkins, Chief Crown Prosecutor
OL,17,Ffor the Crown Prosecution Service said
OL,18,Fthat the CPS and Gwent Police worked
OL,19,Fclosely together throughout the
OL,20,Finvestigation.
