OL,6,FShe added that their "prosecutors have
OL,7,Fworked to establish that there is
OL,8,Fsufficient evidence to bring the case
OL,9,Fto court and that it is in the public
OL,10,Finterest to pursue criminal
OL,11,Fproceedings".
